      "name": "Primary hemolysis validation against FDA pump experimental data",
      "description": "ValidationResult comparing CFD-predicted hemolysis index (HI) to in-vitro measurements across 5 operating points. Mean absolute error 18.3%; normalised RMS error 21.7%. Validation was conducted and this result generated under ModelConfiguration ansys-cfx-15-build-2026-q1-build-7-rc2, which was the release candidate immediately preceding the released solver build. The configuration is considered by the analysis team to be effectively the same build — only a minor linker patch was applied between rc2 and the final release — and validation was not re-executed under the released version to avoid schedule impact.",
